post_text:
Congratulations to the recipients of the Bonhomme Lions Scholarships! This year’s winners include:

Cydney Algee, a student at Hazelwood West High School in Hazelwood School District and North Tech High School ;

Justin Coulter, a student at Hazelwood Central High School;
Haley Meyer, a student at Marquette High in Rockwood School District ;

Raymond Soto, a student at Lindbergh High School in Lindbergh Schools ;

Ethan Wood, a student at Parkway West High School in Parkway Schools .

Congratulations to the scholarship winners: http://www.ssdmo.org/rotate_features/04_20/schol_camp/lions_scholarship.html

